NAME: MEASUREMENT_AGE
DESCRIPTION: age of last measurement in seconds ( saturating at 255)

NAME: WHEN_BYTE_0
DESCRIPTION: LSB byte of uptime at time of measurement

NAME: WHEN_BYTE_1
DESCRIPTION: next to LSB byte of uptime at time of measurement

NAME: WHEN_BYTE_2
DESCRIPTION: next to next to  LSB byte of uptime at time of measurement

NAME: WHEN_BYTE_3
DESCRIPTION: MSB byte of uptime at time of measurement

NAME: WRITE_GPIOS
column5: then send values. Set mask to 0 to not change (then values are don't care or optional). Will read back previous value."
